dct_title_s: Norfolciae descriptio: The description of Norfolk; Amstelodami, apud Ioannem Ianssonium.; Description of Norfolk
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Ships and a sea monster are in the ocean. Title cartouche includes fruit and a face. This state was publshed in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636 and 1637. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 47 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
